snippet.title: Akane | Gameplay Trailer | Nintendo Switch
snippet.description:
There will be no happy ending this time. The only thing that matters now is how great your kill streak is before you go down.
Discover special skills, wield your loyal katana, equip diverse weapons and equipment of your choice and make your last night unforgettable!

Pre-order now! ⏩ http://bit.ly/AkaneeShop
